1.1.1.1
log
@import odt2txt 0.4

odt2txt is a simple converter from OpenDocument Text to plain text. It's
a command-line tool which extracts the text out of OpenDocument Texts
produced by OpenOffice.org, StarOffice, KOffice and others.
@
